---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | Trillionir" canonicalUrl="https://thetrillionair.me/privacy">
  <article>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <section>
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>This privacy policy explains how Trillionir.me collects, uses, and protects your information.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>This is a static portfolio site. We do not actively collect personal data. However:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Visitors may contact me via external links (email, social media)</li>
        <li>Server logs may record IP addresses and page requests</li>
        <li>This site does not set or read browser cookies</li>
        <li>Browser localStorage stores your admin panel edits locally only</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Contact information is only used to respond to inquiries</li>
        <li>Server logs help monitor site performance and security</li>
        <li>Remote admin sync requests are sent without cookies or credentials</li>
        <li>Admin localStorage data never leaves your device</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>This site may integrate with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Back4App</strong> - For potential backend features (Parse Server)</li>
        <li><strong>CDN/Hosting</strong> - Standard web hosting infrastructure</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Each service has its own privacy policy. We are not responsible for third-party privacy practices.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Security</h2>
      <p>We employ standard security practices:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>HTTPS encryption for all traffic</li>
        <li>Content Security Policy headers</li>
        <li>No storage of sensitive user data</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>As this site collects minimal data, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Request what data is stored about you</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Opt-out of contact via provided means</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this privacy policy? Reach out via the <a href="/">social links on the homepage</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Updates</h2>
      <p>This policy may change. Updates will be posted here with the effective date.</p>
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> April 15, 2026</p>
    </section>
  </article>

  <style>
    article {
      max-width: 65ch;
      margin: 0 auto;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    h1 {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    h2 {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    section {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    ul {
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    a {
      color: var(--accent, #0ea5e9);
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
